1985年1月，SIG Sauer在[[弗吉尼亚州|維吉尼亞州]]泰森角成立了子公司'''SIGARMS'''，最初是要將P220和P230出口到美國。兩年后，該公司搬到[[弗吉尼亚州|維吉尼亞州]]赫恩登，在此建立更具規模的工廠，並推出了[[SIG_P220手槍|P225]]、[[SIG_P226半自動手槍|P226]]和[[SIG_P226半自動手槍|P228]]<ref name="HaasZwoll2003">{{Cite book|last=Haas|first=Frank De|last2=Zwoll|first2=Wayne|title=Bolt Action Rifles|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tuVUMLRE47UC&pg=PA2|date=31 October 2003|publisher=Krause Publications|location=Iola, Wisconsin|isbn=0-87349-660-4|pages=2–3}}</ref>。SIGARMS於1990年遷至[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布夏州]][[埃克塞特_(新罕布什尔州)|埃克塞特]]，並建立了生產設施，於1992年開始生產[[SIG_P226半自動手槍|P229]]。 

SIG剩餘的槍械業務<ref name="Ayoob2012">{{Cite book|last=Ayoob|first=Massad|title=Massad Ayoob's Greatest Handguns of the World|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JYmgHFwqT2gC&pg=PA237|date=29 May 2012|publisher=F+W Media|location=Iola, Wisconsin|isbn=978-1-4402-2877-3|pages=237–238}}</ref><ref name="GrässlinHarrich2015">{{Cite book|last=Grässlin|date=2015-09-28|year=|accessdate=2017-12-02|pages=18–19|isbn=978-3-641-18226-7|language=de|publisher=Heyne Verlag|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QBcnCgAAQBAJ&pg=PT18#v=onepage&q&f=false|first=Jürgen|trans-title=Network of Death: The criminal links between arms industry and authorities|title=Netzwerk des Todes: Die kriminellen Verflechtungen von Waffenindustrie und Behörden|first3=Danuta|last3=Harrich-Zandberg|first2=Daniel|last2=Harrich|location=|archive-date=2020-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200613162045/https://books.google.com/books?id=QBcnCgAAQBAJ&pg=PT18#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>，於2000年10月被出售予L＆O Holding的Michael Lüke和Thomas Ortmeier，並改稱為[[瑞士軍工|Swiss Arms]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Swiss Arms: Overview|url=http://www.swissarms.ch/en/|accessdate=2 December 2017|author=|date=|format=|work=swissarms.ch|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2019-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204084352/http://www.swissarms.ch/en/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而產品則仍使用SIG Sauer品牌。根據行政總裁Ron Cohen的說法，在2004年該公司只剩下130名員工，公司幾乎破產。Cohen决定把在美國市場很受歡迎的[[AR-15半自動步槍|AR-15]]引入成為公司的產品，認為這樣可以挽救公司。2019年底，Swiss Arms更名為'''SIG Sauer AG'''<ref>{{Cite web|title=Zefix – Central Business Name Index|url=https://www.zefix.ch/en/search/entity/list/firm/536506?name=SIG%20SAUER%20AG&searchType=exact|accessdate=2020-01-25|author=|date=|format=|work=www.zefix.ch|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200606060853/https://www.zefix.ch/en/search/entity/list/firm/536506?name=SIG%20SAUER%20AG&searchType=exact|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

2007年，美國的SIGARMS更名為'''SIG Sauer Inc.'''<ref name="Ramage2008">{{Cite book|last=Ramage|first=Ken|title=Guns Illustrated 2009|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0pSA2xVGZVYC&pg=PA30|date=2008-11-19|publisher=F+W Media, Inc|isbn=0-89689-673-0|page=30|year=|location=|pages=}}</ref>。因此SIG Sauer便出現兩家姊妹公司，一家在美國[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布夏州]]{{link-en|紐因頓|Newington, New Hampshire}}，另一家在[[北德國|德國北部]][[石勒苏益格-荷尔斯泰因|什勒斯維希-霍爾斯坦]][[埃肯弗德|埃肯弗德]]。自從SIG Sauer Inc.成立以來，所有新的SIG Sauer產品都在美國設計。到了2016年，SIG Sauer Inc.擁有1000多名員工，每年銷售超過43,000支槍械<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.newsweek.com/sig-sauer-orlando-shooting-omar-mateen-assault-rifles-474972|title=This is how SIG Sauer cashed in on selling assault rifles|date=2016-06-27|work=Newsweek|quote="It was a company on the verge of bankruptcy and about two seconds away from imploding," company CEO Ron Cohen recalled in a 2010 profile in Management Today. Then, Cohen made a swift decision that would save the company and turn it into the No. 4 gun manufacturer in America: He turned the company’s sites onto "AR-style" assault rifles that would be marketed to civilians.... In 2004 the company had a mere 130 employees. ... A decade later it sold 43,141 guns in a single year and today has more than 1,000 employees in manufacturing facilities across the country.|author=Eric Markowitz|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|archive-date=2020-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610001419/https://www.newsweek.com/sig-sauer-orlando-shooting-omar-mateen-assault-rifles-474972|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

據SIG Sauer的說法，美國有三分之一的[[美國警察|執法部門]]使用SIG出品的槍械<ref>{{Cite web|title=Military|url=https://www.sigsauer.com/usage/pro/military/|accessdate=2017-12-02|author=|date=|format=|work=sigsauer.com|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417104701/https://www.sigsauer.com/usage/pro/military/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。SIG Sauer亦有一所位於[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布夏州]]埃平，名為'''SIG Sauer學院'''（SIG Sauer Academy）的槍械訓練學校，課程由經驗豐富的導師講授，其中許多具有軍事/警察背景<ref name="HaasZwoll2003">{{Cite book|last=Haas|first=Frank De|last2=Zwoll|first2=Wayne|title=Bolt Action Rifles|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tuVUMLRE47UC&pg=PA2|date=31 October 2003|publisher=Krause Publications|location=Iola, Wisconsin|isbn=0-87349-660-4|pages=2–3}}</ref>。SIG Sauer亦為槍械和運動用品行業生產多種配件<ref name="Officer-Sig Sauer Products">{{Cite web|title=Sig Sauer Inc.|url=http://www.officer.com/company/10030225/sig-sauer-inc|accessdate=2017-02-28|author=|date=|format=|work=officer.com|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2017-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170726214720/http://www.officer.com/company/10030225/sig-sauer-inc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

SIG Sauer在2020年[[SHOT_Show|SHOT Show]]展出了其新一代抑制器，採用[[3D打印|3D列印]]成型，並分別有使用[[钛|鈦]]的手槍抑制器和使用[[英高鎳合金|英高鎳合金]]的步槍抑制器<ref>{{Cite web|title=SILENCER SATURDAY #109: The 2020 SHOT Suppressor Show|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2020/01/25/2020-suppressor-show/|accessdate=2020-08-11|date=2020-01-25|last=Pete|work=The Firearm Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404094644/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2020/01/25/2020-suppressor-show/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

