2020年10月8日，美國陸軍宣佈SIG Sauer勝出了直視瞄具（{{Lang-en|Direct View Optics}}，簡稱DVO）標案，將向陸軍供應最多120,000套1-6倍精確倍率瞄具，以用於[[M4卡賓槍|M4A1]]上並取代[[先進戰鬥光學瞄準鏡|M150步槍戰鬥瞄具]]，全案總值77,168,400美元<ref>{{Cite web|title=US Army Awards SIG Sauer Optics Major Contract for Direct View Optic|url=https://www.overtdefense.com/2020/10/08/us-army-awards-sig-sauer-optics-major-contract-for-direct-view-optic/|accessdate=2020-10-09|author=Matthew Moss|date=2020-10-08|format=|work=The Firearm Blog|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119023038/https://www.overtdefense.com/2020/10/08/us-army-awards-sig-sauer-optics-major-contract-for-direct-view-optic/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。SIG Sauer在2020年11月9日公佈獲選的為泥色TANGO6T 1-6x24 DVO，配有DWLR6準星圖，並採用ALPHA4鏡座<ref>{{Cite web|title=Magazine - SIG SAUER TANGO6T Riflescope Selected by U.S. Department of Defense for Direct View Optic (DVO)|url=https://www.sigsauer.com/blog/sig-sauer-tango6t-riflescope-selected-by-us-department-of-defense-for-direct-view-optic-dvo|accessdate=2020-11-14|work=www.sigsauer.com|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116091401/https://www.sigsauer.com/blog/sig-sauer-tango6t-riflescope-selected-by-us-department-of-defense-for-direct-view-optic-dvo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而同系列的TANGO6早已被美國陸軍採用在[[HK417自動步槍|M110A1 SDMR]]上<ref>{{Cite web|title=SIG SAUER TANGO6 1-6×24 Selected for US Army Designated Marksman Rifle -|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2018/05/17/sig-sauer-tango6-1-6x24-designated-marksman-rifle/|accessdate=2020-11-14|date=2018-05-17|work=The Firearm Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126183426/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2018/05/17/sig-sauer-tango6-1-6x24-designated-marksman-rifle/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及被[[美国特种作战司令部|USSOCOM]]採用為第二焦鏡準星班用可變倍率瞄具（{{Lang-en|Squad-Variable Powered Scopes}}，簡稱SVPS）<ref>{{Cite web|title=US SOCOM Selects SIG Sauer TANGO6 For Squad-Variable Powered Scopes (SFP) -|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2018/10/15/socom-tango6-svps/|accessdate=2020-11-14|date=2018-10-15|work=The Firearm Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411104757/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2018/10/15/socom-tango6-svps/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

